# Assets Secured Lending Amount

## identifier
de13299

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for the loans that the lending institution has extended and are collateralised by legal rights to specifically designated assets owned by the borrowing institution which the lending institution can use and for which the lending institution can claim ownership to in the case of default by the borrower.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.SecuredLending.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.18
- period=instant
